The paper deals with computer vision tasks such as image captioning and visual question answering, which are typically categorized under cs.CV. The paper also proposes a method of incorporating high-level semantic concepts and external knowledge, which are relevant to sub-categories such as cs.CL (computational linguistics), cs.AI (artificial intelligence), and cs.LG (machine learning). Additionally, the paper uses information retrieval techniques to extract information from a general knowledge base, which is relevant to cs.IR (information retrieval).
